The controversies in a viral sex video clip of singer, Tiwa Savage are yet to abate. The activities in the video have been used as one of the questions in an examination paper in a university.   It takes a strong man to love fat women- Lepacious Bose     Lagos heads to US for Red line trains     I stand with Mompha, says Bobrisky   In the first-semester examination 2020/2021 academic session of the Federal University, Lafia, Nassarawa State, Faculty of Arts, Department of English and Literary Studies Course code: English 314; Course title: Literature, Popular culture, and Mass media, the question number two reads: ‘‘Tiwa Savage’s notorious video trended in 2021. What is the connection between musical lyrics and poetry?’’